      <title>杠杆科技押注在吸纳 20 亿美元后惨遭失败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/leveraged-tech-bets-get-crushed-after-drawing-in-2-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在最近人工智能推动的科技股大涨期间，逢低买入是一种制胜策略。但现在它却适得其反——对于那些通过加大赌注来扩大回报的人来说尤其痛苦。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/leveraged-tech-bets-get-crushed-after-drawing-in-2-billion</guid>
